procedureJavascriptCode.name: New Procedure Javascript Code
procedureJavascriptCode.code:
// Get the Tweets

let tweets = record.current
const vader = SA.nodeModules.vaderSentiment

variable.compoundScores = []
variable.negScores = []
variable.posScores = []
variable.neuScores = []

for (let i = 0; i < tweets.data.length; i++) {
    let scores = vader.SentimentIntensityAnalyzer.polarity_scores(tweets.data[i].text)
    variable.compoundScores.push(scores.compound)
    variable.negScores.push(scores.neg)
    variable.neuScores.push(scores.neu)
    variable.posScores.push(scores.pos)
}

variable.compound = variable.compoundScores.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0) / variable.compoundScores.length
variable.neg = variable.negScores.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0) / variable.negScores.length
variable.neu = variable.neuScores.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0) / variable.neuScores.length
variable.pos = variable.posScores.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0) / variable.posScores.length
